  }
  $ g++ -Wall -Wextra -Wconversion -Werror unsigned.cpp 
  $ ./a.out 
  x = 4294967295
</code></pre>
No error, no warning. The two are not really distinct types. See the link I posted above for more argumentation along these lines.
